thread.title: Suzy Sioux
thread.title_full: Country Attire Ltd. (www.countryattire.com) reviewed by Suzy Sioux

author: Suzy Sioux
title: Suzy Sioux
text: Very good service from start to finish. Ordered a Barbour jacket for my husband - best price after comparing with many others retailers. Ordered Sunday night, jacket arrived Tuesday morning, delivery was free. You can't get better than that, lovely jacket too, very pleased!
